==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Assurer
<hw>As*sur"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who assures. Specifically: One who insures against loss; an insurer or
underwriter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who takes out a life assurance policy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Assurgency</ent>⟦br⟧
